<h2 id="write-contents">Write Contents</h2>

<p>Markdown ë¬¸ë²•ìœ¼ë¡œ ì±… ë³¸ë¬¸ì„ ì“°ì. ì‹¤í—˜ ì§‘í•„ì—ì„œëŠ” <code class="highlighter-rouge">_draft/chapter1.md</code>, <code class="highlighter-rouge">_draft/chapter2.md</code> 2ê°œì˜ Markdown íŒŒì¼ì„ ë§Œë“¤ì—ˆë‹¤. ì±…ì— ì“°ì´ëŠ” ì´ë¯¸ì§€ íŒŒì¼ë“¤ì€ <code class="highlighter-rouge">_draft/images</code> ì— ë„£ì—ˆë‹¤.</p>

<div class="language-markdown highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c">&lt;!--_draft/chapter1.md--&gt;</span>

<span class="gh"># An exhibit of Markdown</span>

This note demonstrates some of what <span class="p">[</span><span class="nv">Markdown</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="ss">1</span><span class="p">]</span> is capable of doing.

<span class="ge">*Note: Feel free to play with this page. Unlike regular notes, this doesn't automatically save itself.*</span>

<span class="p">![](</span><span class="sx">images/markdown_editor.png</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="p">[</span><span class="ss">1</span><span class="p">]:</span> <span class="sx">http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-markdown highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c">&lt;!--_draft/chapter2.md--&gt;</span>

<span class="gh"># An exhibit of Markdown</span>

<span class="gu">## Unordered list</span>
<span class="p">
-</span> An item
<span class="p">-</span> Another item[^1]
<span class="p">-</span> Yet another item
<span class="p">-</span> And there's more...

<span class="p">[</span><span class="ss">^1</span><span class="p">]:</span> <span class="sx">Another</span> Item_ http://blog.appkr.dev 
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">README.md</code> ì™€ <code class="highlighter-rouge">SUMMARY.md</code> 2ê°œì˜ íŒŒì¼ì€ Gitbook Mandatory ì´ë¯€ë¡œ ê¼­ ë§Œë“¤ì–´ ì£¼ì–´ì•¼ í•œë‹¤. (í”„ë¡œì íŠ¸ ë£¨íŠ¸ì— ë§Œë“ ë‹¤.)</p>

<div class="language-markdown highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c">&lt;!--README.md--&gt;</span>

<span class="gh"># My Book</span>

by appkr
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-markdown highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c">&lt;!--SUMMARY.md--&gt;</span>

<span class="gh"># Table of Contents</span>
<span class="p">
-</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="nv">Chapter 1</span><span class="p">](</span><span class="sx">_draft/chapter1.md</span><span class="p">)</span>
